label: [{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"禽病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 随着养鸡业的迅速发展，购销旺盛，交流频繁，造成当前禽病发生与流行有如下特点。

label: [{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"禽病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 1.禽病的种类增多：现有80多种，以传染病最多，约占75%。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"禽病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":18,"text":"鸡传染性贫血","labels":["disease"]},{"start":19,"end":22,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"肾型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":36,"text":"腺胃型传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":37,"end":44,"text":"鸡病毒性关节炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":45,"end":50,"text":"包含体肝炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":51,"end":56,"text":"肠毒综合征","labels":["disease"]},{"start":57,"end":64,"text":"产蛋减少综合征","labels":["disease"]},{"start":65,"end":72,"text":"雏鸭病毒性肝炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":73,"end":80,"text":"番鸭细小病毒病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":81,"end":88,"text":"鸭传染性浆膜炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":89,"end":96,"text":"肉鸡腹水综合征","labels":["disease"]},{"start":97,"end":102,"text":"隐孢子虫病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 2.新的禽病不断出现：如鸡传染性贫血、禽流感、肾型和腺胃型传染性支气管炎、鸡病毒性关节炎、包含体肝炎、肠毒综合征、产蛋减少综合征、雏鸭病毒性肝炎、番鸭细小病毒病、鸭传染性浆膜炎、肉鸡腹水综合征、隐孢子虫病等。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":7,"end":13,"text":"鸡传染性贫血","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"肾传支","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 特别是禽流感、鸡传染性贫血和肾传支。

label: [{"start":4,"end":9,"text":"非典型发病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":11,"end":17,"text":"非典型新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":18,"end":22,"text":"法氏囊病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":23,"end":28,"text":"马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 3.出现非典型发病：如非典型新城疫、法氏囊病、马立克氏病等，使某些原有的旧病以新的面貌出现，所以，诊断防治应格外注意。

label: [{"start":4,"end":9,"text":"细菌性疾病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"寄生虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"大肠杆菌","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":30,"text":"沙门氏菌","labels":["disease"]},{"start":31,"end":36,"text":"绿脓杆菌病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":37,"end":41,"text":"支原体病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":42,"end":50,"text":"小鸭传染性浆膜炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":51,"end":55,"text":"鸡球虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":56,"end":63,"text":"鸡住白细胞虫病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 4.某些细菌性疾病和寄生虫病的危害加大，如大肠杆菌、沙门氏菌、绿脓杆菌病、支原体病、小鸭传染性浆膜炎、鸡球虫病、鸡住白细胞虫病等。

label: [{"start":19,"end":27,"text":"破坏免疫系统疾病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":28,"end":31,"text":"法氏囊","labels":["disease"]},{"start":32,"end":37,"text":"传染性贫血","labels":["disease"]},{"start":44,"end":47,"text":"抗菌药","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 这些病原体存在广泛，传播途径广，再加上破坏免疫系统疾病(法氏囊、传染性贫血)的流行，滥用抗菌药，所以上述疫病容易发生。

label: [{"start":38,"end":41,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":42,"end":45,"text":"法氏囊","labels":["disease"]},{"start":46,"end":53,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":54,"end":56,"text":"流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":57,"end":62,"text":"大肠杆菌病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":63,"end":69,"text":"慢性呼吸道病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 5.混合感染使疾病复杂化并发病、继发感染和混合感染的病例增多，如混合感染的有新城疫和法氏囊、传染性支气管炎、流感、大肠杆菌病、慢性呼吸道病；

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"大肠杆菌病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":11,"text":"沙门氏菌病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":18,"text":"慢性呼吸道病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 大肠杆菌病和沙门氏菌病、慢性呼吸道病等。

label: [{"start":2,"end":9,"text":"营养代谢性疾病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":10,"end":15,"text":"中毒性疾病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 6.营养代谢性疾病和中毒性疾病增多。

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"免疫鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: 8.免疫鸡群仍然发病。

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"病毒性疾病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":11,"text":"马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":16,"text":"法氏囊病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":24,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":25,"end":30,"text":"传染性喉炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":31,"end":36,"text":"流行性感冒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":37,"end":40,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":41,"end":45,"text":"脑脊髓炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":46,"end":52,"text":"病毒性关节炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":53,"end":58,"text":"减蛋综合征","labels":["disease"]},{"start":59,"end":61,"text":"鸡痘","labels":["disease"]},{"start":64,"end":67,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 病毒性疾病：马立克氏病、法氏囊病、传染性支气管炎、传染性喉炎、流行性感冒、新城疫、脑脊髓炎、病毒性关节炎、减蛋综合征、鸡痘。其中新城疫为重中之重。

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"细菌性疾病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":11,"text":"大肠杆菌病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":17,"text":"沙门氏菌病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":18,"end":23,"text":"葡萄球菌病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":27,"end":32,"text":"巴氏杆菌病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":33,"end":37,"text":"链球菌病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":38,"end":43,"text":"绿脓杆菌病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 细菌性疾病：大肠杆菌病、沙门氏菌病、葡萄球菌病，其他如巴氏杆菌病、链球菌病、绿脓杆菌病也不可忽视。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"支原体","labels":["disease"]},{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"球虫病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":18,"text":"霉菌毒素感染","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 支原体和球虫病危害很大。霉菌毒素感染越来越多。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"营养代谢性疾病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":16,"text":"B族维生素缺乏症","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":30,"text":"重金属量超标","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":23,"text":"钙磷比例失调","labels":["disease"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"痛风症","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 营养代谢性疾病：B族维生素缺乏症，钙磷比例失调，重金属量超标、痛风症等经常发生。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":5,"end":11,"text":"A型流感病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":29,"end":38,"text":"高度致死性的传染病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":44,"end":46,"text":"鸡瘟","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":15,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"禽类","labels":["type"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"急性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"热性","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 禽流感是由A型流感病毒引起的鸡和其他禽类的一种急性、热性、高度致死性的传染病，历史上称为鸡瘟。

label: [{"start":5,"end":10,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":11,"end":16,"text":"消化道症状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":22,"text":"头颈部水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"麻痹","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":17,"end":20,"text":"头颈部","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 主要特征为呼吸道症状、消化道症状和头颈部水肿、麻痹。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 禽流感传播迅速，危害严重，给养鸡业带来极大威胁。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"血清型","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 有的血清型还可感染人类和其他家畜，是公共卫生上的重要疫病，应引起特别关注。

label: [{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":34,"text":"正黏病毒科禽流感病毒属A型流感病毒","labels":["disease"]}]
text: (一)病原学特征：禽流感的病原体是正黏病毒科禽流感病毒属A型流感病毒。

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"禽流感病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":36,"end":41,"text":"禽流感病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"鸡胚","labels":["type"]},{"start":46,"end":50,"text":"组织细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":26,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":32,"end":35,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 禽流感病毒有囊膜，膜的棘突上有血凝素(H),可凝集鸡和其他动物的红细胞，禽流感病毒可在鸡胚和组织细胞中繁殖。

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"禽流感病毒","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 禽流感病毒另一重要成分是神经氨酸酶(N)。

label: [{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 自20世纪90年代以来，全球很多国家发生禽流感并分离到不同亚型的毒株。

label: [{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 我国存在的禽流感亚型主要是H9N2、H5N1和H9N7亚型。

label: [{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 由于自然环境的变迁和饲养环境的改变，以及人类对禽流感防控意识的加强，可以预料，还会发生新的毒株亚型，构成对养鸡业的灾难和对人类健康的危害。

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"禽流感病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":19,"text":"酸性消毒药","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 禽流感病毒抵抗力较强，尤其对酸性消毒药，而且耐低温(在一20℃可存活几年)、耐潮湿；

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"鼻腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 存在于鼻腔和粪便中的病毒。

label: [{"start":56,"end":61,"text":"禽流感病毒","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 在干燥的尘埃中可存活两周：不耐高温，加热56℃30分钟、70℃2分钟即可灭活，因此，经过充分加热后的食品中不存在禽流感病毒；

label: [{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"直射日光","labels":["control"]}]
text: 对紫外线也敏感，直射日光40～48小时即灭活；

label: [{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"消毒药","labels":["drug"]},{"start":18,"end":22,"text":"含氯制剂","labels":["drug"]},{"start":23,"end":28,"text":"酚类消毒药","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 酸性以外的消毒药均能很快将其杀死，如含氯制剂和酚类消毒药；

label: [{"start":2,"end":7,"text":"禽流感病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"囊膜病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"去污剂","labels":["drug"]},{"start":18,"end":24,"text":"脂溶性的药剂","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 由于禽流感病毒是囊膜病毒，对去污剂等脂溶性的药剂敏感。

label: [{"start":7,"end":10,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 1.发病季节：禽流感四季均可发生，但以早春、晚秋以及冬季天气寒冷和气候多变季节多发。

label: [{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"禽流感毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":27,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":35,"end":36,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 这是因为禽流感毒耐低温，可随风和候鸟迁徙传播，气候对鸡本身的应激刺激使鸡的抵抗力降低。

label: [{"start":18,"end":21,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 近年来的实践证明，炎热的夏季也可发生禽流感，同样会造成重大的经济损失。

label: [{"start":15,"end":18,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"禽类","labels":["type"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":33,"text":"分泌物","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"鼻涕","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"眼泪","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"唾液","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":45,"end":48,"text":"排泄物","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":49,"end":51,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":54,"end":56,"text":"血液","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 2.传染来源病鸡和带毒的禽类是禽流感的传染来源，它们的羽毛和分泌物(鼻涕、眼泪、唾液等)、排泄物(粪便)以及血液中含有大量病毒。

label: [{"start":6,"end":7,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"禽类","labels":["type"]},{"start":27,"end":28,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"火鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":46,"end":47,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":55,"end":59,"text":"产蛋鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: 3.易感动物鸡、鸭、鹅、鸽子等多种禽类都有易感性，其中鸡和火鸡最易感，不同日龄、性别和品种的鸡都可感染发病，以产蛋鸡群最多发生，而且最先发生。

label: [{"start":6,"end":9,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":29,"end":32,"text":"分泌物","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":33,"end":36,"text":"排泄物","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":57,"end":59,"text":"野禽","labels":["type"]},{"start":82,"end":85,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 4.传播途径禽流感可直接接触传播和间接接触传播，如被患病者分泌物、排泄物污染的饲料、饮水、空气和用具构成传播因素，野禽和水禽以及候鸟的迁徙、观赏鸟类的销售运输，也是禽流感的传播途径。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":10,"end":13,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":6,"end":9,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":24,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 禽流感主要经呼吸道和消化道传播。实验证明，禽流感可垂直传播。

label: [{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"温和型禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"治疗","labels":["control"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":50,"end":54,"text":"禽流感毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":85,"end":92,"text":"高致病性禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":73,"end":74,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 对于温和型禽流感(如我国发生的H9N2亚型),由于经过缓慢，采取治疗、消毒等措施，可促使病毒变异，使禽流感毒的抵抗力加强，毒力加大，可能成为下一批鸡的危险疫源地，从而引起高致病性禽流感的发生。

label: [{"start":26,"end":27,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":45,"end":47,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: (三)临床症状：其临床症状依感染病毒毒株的毒力大小，鸡的种类、日龄，有无并发症、继发感染，鸡群营养状况、饲养管理精细程度，环境因素的优劣以及采取的防控措施是否得当等的不同而表现各异。

label: [{"start":7,"end":16,"text":"高致病性禽流感病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":19,"end":22,"text":"急性型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":27,"end":31,"text":"产蛋鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":36,"end":40,"text":"暴发流行","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 在正常情况下，高致病性禽流感病毒所致的急性型，主要侵害产蛋鸡群，鸡群可能暴发流行，潜伏期甚短，多不见症状而迅速死亡。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"温和型禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"精神沉郁","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"独处一隅","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":18,"end":22,"text":"垂头缩颈","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":23,"end":27,"text":"闭眼似睡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":28,"end":33,"text":"采食量减少","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":34,"end":38,"text":"鼻腔肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":36,"end":38,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":44,"text":"分泌物增多","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":45,"end":50,"text":"眼结膜充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":51,"end":53,"text":"流泪","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":54,"end":58,"text":"头部肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":56,"end":58,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":61,"end":66,"text":"髯呈紫红色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":63,"end":66,"text":"紫红色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":71,"end":76,"text":"前胸部肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":74,"end":76,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":77,"end":86,"text":"腿部无毛处有出血斑","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":83,"end":86,"text":"出血斑","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":20,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":22,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":25,"text":"眼","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"鼻腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":45,"end":48,"text":"眼结膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":54,"end":56,"text":"头部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":61,"end":62,"text":"髯","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":59,"end":60,"text":"冠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":67,"end":70,"text":"咽喉部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":71,"end":74,"text":"前胸部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":77,"end":79,"text":"腿部","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 温和型禽流感表现精神沉郁，独处一隅，垂头缩颈，闭眼似睡，采食量减少，鼻腔肿胀，分泌物增多，眼结膜充血，流泪，头部肿胀，冠、髯呈紫红色，咽喉部、前胸部肿胀，腿部无毛处有出血斑。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":7,"end":10,"text":"有啰音","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"张口伸颈","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":25,"text":"发生尖叫声","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":14,"end":15,"text":"口","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":17,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病鸡呼吸困难，有啰音，有时张口伸颈，有时发生尖叫声。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"腹泻","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":17,"text":"绿色相间的稀粪","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":6,"end":7,"text":"黄","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":8,"end":9,"text":"白","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"绿色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":16,"end":17,"text":"粪","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病鸡腹泻，拉黄、白、绿色相间的稀粪，常带有未消化的饲料。

label: [{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"神经症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"兴奋","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"癫狂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"痉挛","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":30,"text":"作圆圈运动","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"四肢麻痹","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"麻痹","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":36,"end":40,"text":"运动失调","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":41,"end":46,"text":"产蛋率下降","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":90,"end":93,"text":"软壳蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":94,"end":97,"text":"褪色蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":98,"end":101,"text":"畸形蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":102,"end":105,"text":"特小蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":106,"end":112,"text":"蛋的品质低劣","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"四肢","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":68,"end":70,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: 病后期，出现明显的神经症状，兴奋、癫狂和痉挛，有的作圆圈运动，四肢麻痹，运动失调，产蛋率下降20%～50%,甚至达90%以上，下降幅度与鸡群状态、防控措施是否得当有关，较长时间出现软壳蛋、褪色蛋、畸形蛋、特小蛋，蛋的品质低劣。

label: [{"start":19,"end":22,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]}]
text: (四)病理变化：1.高致病性毒株引起的禽流感可见以下一种或几种病理变化。

label: [{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"头面部水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"鼻窦炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":15,"end":18,"text":"髯充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"发紫","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"头面部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":14,"text":"冠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":16,"text":"髯","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (1)头面部水肿，鼻窦炎，冠、髯充血、发紫。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"喉部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":3,"end":9,"text":"喉部有出血点","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":9,"text":"出血点","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"气管充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":25,"text":"内有黏性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":43,"text":"两侧支气管内充满黄色干酪样物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":43,"text":"干酪样物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (2)喉部有出血点，气管充血或出血，内有黏性分泌物，有时见两侧支气管内充满黄色干酪样物。

label: [{"start":12,"end":19,"text":"黏膜面有出血点","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"出血点","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":39,"text":"腹部脂肪有针尖大小的点状出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":39,"text":"点状出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":3,"end":11,"text":"内脏器官的浆膜面","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"黏膜面","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"心冠脂肪","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":29,"text":"腹部脂肪","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (3)内脏器官的浆膜面和黏膜面有出血点，心冠脂肪、腹部脂肪有针尖大小的点状出血。

label: [{"start":3,"end":9,"text":"腺胃乳头出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":19,"text":"黏膜上有脓性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":19,"text":"脓性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":28,"text":"肌胃角质膜易剥离","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":28,"text":"易剥离","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":36,"text":"皱褶处有出血斑","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"腺胃乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":25,"text":"肌胃角质膜","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (4)腺胃乳头出血，黏膜上有脓性分泌物，肌胃角质膜易剥离，皱褶处有出血斑。

label: [{"start":6,"end":13,"text":"广泛性出血炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":23,"text":"充满脓性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":28,"text":"胶冻状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"肠道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (5)肠道有广泛性出血炎症，有时充满脓性分泌物，呈胶冻状。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":16,"text":"腹腔内有破裂的卵黄","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":16,"text":"破裂的卵黄","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":26,"text":"典型的腹膜炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":36,"text":"大量的干酪样物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"腹腔","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (6)产蛋鸡的腹腔内有破裂的卵黄，或出现典型的腹膜炎，并有大量的干酪样物。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"卵泡变性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"变性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"血肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":21,"text":"严重的卵泡变黑","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"变黑","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"卵泡","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"卵泡","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 卵泡变性、坏死、充血、血肿，严重的卵泡变黑。

label: [{"start":4,"end":10,"text":"子宫黏膜水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":23,"text":"白色黏稠分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":30,"text":"胶冻状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"子宫黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 输卵管和子宫黏膜水肿、出血，内有白色黏稠分泌物。有时呈胶冻状。

label: [{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"颅骨出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":28,"text":"胰腺管有灰白色坏死灶","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":28,"text":"坏死灶","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":25,"text":"灰白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"胸肌","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"腿肌","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"心外膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"颅骨","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":18,"end":21,"text":"胰腺管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (7)胸肌、腿肌、心外膜、颅骨出血，胰腺管有灰白色坏死灶。

label: [{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"低致病性毒株","labels":["disease"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 2.低致病性毒株引起的禽流感可见以下一种或几种病理变化。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"病死鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"机体消瘦","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"严重脱水","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":22,"text":"皮肤干燥","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"干燥","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":27,"text":"羽毛蓬乱","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"蓬乱","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":32,"text":"冠髯发紫","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"发紫","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":39,"text":"肿胀变厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"变厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":42,"end":47,"text":"头面部肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":45,"end":47,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"皮肤","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"冠髯","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"肿胀","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":42,"end":45,"text":"头面部","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (1)病死鸡常见机体消瘦，严重脱水，皮肤干燥，羽毛蓬乱，冠髯发紫，有时肿胀变厚，有时头面部肿胀。

label: [{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"鼻腔有黏液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"黏液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":14,"text":"喉头有出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":20,"text":"附有黏液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":26,"text":"气管环充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":31,"text":"黏膜水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":36,"text":"浆液性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":43,"text":"干酪样分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":44,"end":50,"text":"气囊增厚混浊","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":46,"end":50,"text":"增厚混浊","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":53,"end":56,"text":"纤维性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":57,"end":63,"text":"干酪性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"鼻腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"喉头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":24,"text":"气管环","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":44,"end":46,"text":"气囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (2)鼻腔有黏液，喉头有出血，并附有黏液，气管环充血，黏膜水肿，有浆液性或干酪样分泌物，气囊增厚混浊，附有纤维性或干酪性分泌物。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":15,"end":21,"text":"泌尿生殖系统","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (3)产蛋鸡最明显的病理变化在泌尿生殖系统。

label: [{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"卵泡充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"紫黑色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"卵泡变性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"变性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"破裂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"流人腹腔","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":40,"text":"腹膜炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"卵泡","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"卵泡","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"腹腔","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 发病前期，卵泡充血、出血，呈紫黑色，有的卵泡变性、坏死或破裂，流人腹腔形成腹膜炎；

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"输卵管炎性水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"炎性水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"质地脆弱","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"极易撕裂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":28,"text":"白色胶冻样分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":34,"end":42,"text":"包埋的卵子硬结块","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 输卵管炎性水肿，质地脆弱，极易撕裂，内有白色胶冻样分泌物，有时还可见包埋的卵子硬结块；

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"肾脏肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"变性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":17,"text":"大量的尿酸盐沉积","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":32,"text":"卵泡数量减少","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":32,"text":"数量减少","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"变小","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":44,"text":"米粒样白色颗粒","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"肾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"卵泡","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 肾脏肿大、变性，有大量的尿酸盐沉积。随着疾病的发展，卵泡数量减少，变小，呈米粒样白色颗粒；

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"输卵管变细","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"变细","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"变短","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"萎缩","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"弯曲","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":21,"text":"皱褶的虾样","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":32,"text":"完全丧失了其生理功能","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 输卵管变细、变短、萎缩，呈弯曲、皱褶的虾样，完全丧失了其生理功能。

label: [{"start":9,"end":15,"text":"饲养管理合理","labels":["control"]},{"start":16,"end":22,"text":"防控措施得当","labels":["control"]},{"start":23,"end":29,"text":"及时合理救治","labels":["control"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":39,"end":41,"text":"卵泡","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":68,"end":71,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":72,"end":74,"text":"子宫","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":72,"end":76,"text":"子宫炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":53,"end":55,"text":"变性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":56,"end":58,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 如果病毒毒力不强，饲养管理合理，防控措施得当，及时合理救治，病鸡是可以康复的，卵泡开始新生并逐渐发育，原有变性、坏死部分逐渐萎缩、消失，输卵管、子宫炎症消失，30～60天恢复产蛋。

label: [{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"口腔有黏液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"黏液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":15,"text":"嗦囊充满液体","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"充满液体","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":24,"text":"挤压时流出","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":30,"text":"酸臭味","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"口腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"嗦囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (4)口腔有黏液，嗦囊充满液体，倒提或挤压时流出，具有酸臭味；

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"腺肾乳头出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":13,"text":"脓性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":25,"text":"与肌胃交界处有出血斑点","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"出血斑点","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"腺肾乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"肌胃","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 腺肾乳头出血，有脓性分泌物，与肌胃交界处有出血斑点；

label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"肌胃角质膜易剥离","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"易剥离","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":15,"text":"膜下有出血斑","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"出血斑","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":24,"text":"肌层断面可见出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"肌胃角质膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"膜下","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"肌层","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 肌胃角质膜易剥离，膜下有出血斑，肌层断面可见出血；

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"肠卡他性炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":13,"text":"脓性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":23,"text":"肠黏膜有条纹状出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":23,"text":"条纹状出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"肠黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 肠卡他性炎症，有脓性分泌物，肠黏膜有条纹状出血；

label: [{"start":0,"end":9,"text":"泄硝腔有严重的充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":9,"text":"严重的充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"紫红色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":31,"text":"绿色的稀粪","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"绿色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":25,"text":"白","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":23,"text":"黄","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"泄硝腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":31,"text":"粪","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 泄硝腔有严重的充血、出血，呈紫红色，有时存有黄、白、绿色的稀粪；

label: [{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"出血点","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"出血斑","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"全身脂肪","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 全身脂肪有出血点或出血斑；

label: [{"start":18,"end":21,"text":"出血点","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"内脏器官的浆膜面","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"黏膜面","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 内脏器官的浆膜面和黏膜面有不同程度的出血点；

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"心肌变薄","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"变薄","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"收缩无力","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"心包肥厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"肥厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":15,"end":27,"text":"心包腔常有大量橙黄色积液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":25,"text":"橙黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"积液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"心肌","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"心包","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":18,"text":"心包腔","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 心肌变薄，收缩无力，心包肥厚，心包腔常有大量橙黄色积液；

label: [{"start":9,"end":14,"text":"黄色坏庇灶","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"心外膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":4,"end":5,"text":"肝","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 心外膜和肝表面可见黄色坏庇灶。

label: [{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"鸡新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":25,"end":31,"text":"一氧化碳中毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":32,"end":37,"text":"痢特灵中毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":38,"end":41,"text":"小鹅瘟","labels":["disease"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"鸭瘟","labels":["disease"]},{"start":45,"end":51,"text":"鸭传染性肝炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":52,"end":58,"text":"鸡传染性鼻炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":59,"end":67,"text":"鸡传染性法氏囊病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":68,"end":71,"text":"禽霍乱","labels":["disease"]},{"start":80,"end":83,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 在生产实践中遇到的禽流感，某些临床表现与鸡新城疫、一氧化碳中毒、痢特灵中毒、小鹅瘟、鸭瘟、鸭传染性肝炎、鸡传染性鼻炎、鸡传染性法氏囊病、禽霍乱等相似，尤其容易和新城疫混淆。

label: [{"start":15,"end":18,"text":"病死鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"鼻腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":38,"text":"实质脏器","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 为了确诊，应采病料送检，可采取病死鸡的鼻腔渗出液和气管分泌物、全血、实质脏器等，送至国家指定监测单位进行检测，也可采取急性期或恢复期双份血清送检。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"咳嗽","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: (1)呼吸道异常很难区分，但新城疫初期以咳嗽为主。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":10,"end":13,"text":"橘黄色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":15,"text":"不排橘黄色粪便","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: (2)新城疫病鸡不排橘黄色粪便。

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"颈部胸腺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"胸腺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":35,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"胸腺","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (1)颈部胸腺的病变：新城疫的病变仅在1～4对胸腺，出血或肿大。禽流感的病变在下几对胸腺。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"腿脚部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"胰脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"鳞片出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"胰脏出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":30,"end":33,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"胰脏","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (2)腿脚部鳞片、胰脏病变：禽流感鳞片出血，胰脏出血、坏死。新城疫无此病变。

label: [{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"盲肠扁桃体","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":25,"end":28,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"严重出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: (3)盲肠扁桃体变化：新城疫肿大，坏死或严重出血。禽流感一般不见此病变，个别出现肿大、出血。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"腹膜炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":19,"end":28,"text":"黄色纤维素性腹膜炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"肉鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: (4)腹膜炎病变：感染禽流感时，肉鸡见黄色纤维素性腹膜炎；

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":15,"end":21,"text":"卵黄性腹膜炎","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 蛋鸡发病前期有些变化，后期出现卵黄性腹膜炎。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":19,"end":25,"text":"卵黄性腹膜炎","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 新城疫则不见上述病变，后期可出现轻微的卵黄性腹膜炎。

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"腺胃乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"腺胃乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":24,"text":"腺胃乳头尖部有出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: (5)腺胃乳头的变化：新城疫时腺胃乳头尖部有出血。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":4,"end":10,"text":"腺置乳头基部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":4,"end":13,"text":"腺置乳头基部有出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":20,"text":"整个乳头出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":30,"text":"整个乳胃黏膜发红","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"发红","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"乳胃黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 禽流感时腺置乳头基部有出血或整个乳头出血，或整个乳胃黏膜发红、出血。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"头部","labels":["type"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":13,"end":21,"text":"头部呈苍白色硬肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"苍白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"硬肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":31,"text":"肉垂不单独肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":31,"text":"不单独肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"头部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"肉垂","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (6)头部的变化：禽流感时头部呈苍白色硬肿，一般肉垂不单独肿胀或不肿胀。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"肿头","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"肿脸","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 新城疫时没有肿头、肿脸现象。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"肠道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"肠道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":11,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":40,"end":43,"text":"新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":21,"end":29,"text":"小米粒样的出血点","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"渗血","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: (7)肠道变化：禽流感时肠道有一个或多个像小米粒样的出血点，刀刮有明显渗血感觉。新城疫则没有上述变化。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":19,"text":"头等烈性传染病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":58,"end":61,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":63,"end":78,"text":"及时向当地兽医主管部门报告疫情","labels":["control"]}]
text: 禽流感是人、畜、禽共患的头等烈性传染病，严重威胁养殖业发展和人类健康，是公共卫生极为重要的问题，所以，一且在某地发生禽流感，应及时向当地兽医主管部门报告疫情，以便及时采取措施，扑灭疫病，降低损失。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 根据禽流感流行情况，将其分为四级；

label: [{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"加强饲养管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":8,"end":16,"text":"做好鸡舍保温工作","labels":["control"]},{"start":17,"end":25,"text":"确保鸡舍空气流通","labels":["control"]},{"start":26,"end":32,"text":"供给全价营养","labels":["control"]},{"start":33,"end":38,"text":"清洁的饲料","labels":["control"]},{"start":42,"end":48,"text":"及时清理粪便","labels":["control"]},{"start":49,"end":57,"text":"坚持定期带鸡消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":58,"end":62,"text":"除虫灭鼠","labels":["control"]},{"start":54,"end":55,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":72,"end":74,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 1.加强饲养管理做好鸡舍保温工作，确保鸡舍空气流通，供给全价营养、清洁的饲料和饮水，及时清理粪便，坚持定期带鸡消毒，除虫灭鼠，防止各种应激，提高鸡群自身主动免疫能力。

label: [{"start":2,"end":11,"text":"制定合理的免疫程序","labels":["control"]},{"start":12,"end":23,"text":"选择正规厂家生产的疫苗","labels":["control"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"规范操作","labels":["control"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 2.制定合理的免疫程序：选择正规厂家生产的疫苗，规范操作。

label: [{"start":1,"end":6,"text":"禽流感病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: 因禽流感病毒有很多亚型，疫苗的种类再多，新疫苗的研发速度再快，也赶不上病毒变异的速度，所以，虽然鸡群经过免疫，但仍有感染发病的可能。

label: [{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: 临床实践证明，凡是按时、规范免疫过的鸡群，即使感染发病，也比较轻微。

label: [{"start":2,"end":11,"text":"H9N2亚型禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"蛋鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 蛋鸡H9N2亚型禽流感的参考免疫程序为：7～10日龄首免，35～45日龄二免，开产前2～4周三免，产蛋高峰过后加强免疫一次，在环境严重污染的地区或秋冬季节，可于14周龄前后再免疫一次。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"肉仔鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 肉仔鸡于5日龄免疫一次即可。

label: [{"start":2,"end":10,"text":"加强生物安全措施","labels":["control"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"封闭饲养","labels":["control"]},{"start":18,"end":29,"text":"饲养场应尽量与外界隔绝","labels":["control"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"野禽","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":37,"text":"避免与野禽接触","labels":["control"]},{"start":59,"end":67,"text":"谢绝外来人员入内","labels":["control"]},{"start":68,"end":80,"text":"饲养管理人员注意个人卫生","labels":["control"]},{"start":81,"end":92,"text":"鸡舍和周围环境定期消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":93,"end":103,"text":"粪便要进行生物热消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":105,"end":113,"text":"病鸡及时隔离治疗","labels":["control"]},{"start":115,"end":124,"text":"死鸡及时无害化处理","labels":["control"]},{"start":105,"end":107,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":115,"end":117,"text":"死鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":93,"end":95,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 3.加强生物安全措施，实行封闭饲养：饲养场应尽量与外界隔绝，避免与野禽接触，饲养场内或周围不饲养鸭、鹅、猫、狗等动物，谢绝外来人员入内，饲养管理人员注意个人卫生，鸡舍和周围环境定期消毒，粪便要进行生物热消毒，对病鸡及时隔离治疗，对死鸡及时无害化处理。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":4,"end":10,"text":"特效治疗药物","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 禽流感无特效治疗药物。

label: [{"start":2,"end":9,"text":"低致病性禽流感","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"支持疗法","labels":["control"]},{"start":27,"end":31,"text":"抗病毒药","labels":["drug"]},{"start":32,"end":35,"text":"抗菌药","labels":["drug"]},{"start":49,"end":54,"text":"解热镇痛药","labels":["drug"]},{"start":63,"end":66,"text":"维生素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":72,"end":75,"text":"电解质","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 发现低致病性禽流感病鸡时才采用支持疗法，发病前期可应用抗病毒药、抗菌药控制病情，防止继发感染，配合解热镇痛药缓解症状，同时配合维生素、微量元素、电解质多维等增强抵抗力。

label: [{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"中药制剂","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 后期可用中药制剂，促进恢复。

label: [{"start":11,"end":18,"text":"免疫抑制性药物","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 选用药物时应注意，不用免疫抑制性药物，不用抑制产蛋的药物，不用残留量大的药物，不用易产生抗药性的药物。
